rooms.Name: Mountain Tunnel Entrance
rooms.Description:
As your walking along a mountain seems to rise out of no-where,
blocking your travels to where you were going.  The mountain is to
steep to climb and too long to go around.  Just as you are about to
give up in frustration and turn around, you notice a hole in the 
mountainside hiding behind a rock and some bushes.

rooms.Name: Mountain Tunnel
rooms.Description:
You enter the mountain even though you're not sure it's in your
best interest.  The air seems cooler here and it is a relief from
all the walking you've been doing.  You sniff the air, trying to 
make sure nothing dangerous is in here before you venture farther,
but the only smell that comes to you is the smell of a stream.  Yes,
now that you think of it, you can hear water running off to the north.
It seems to be calm here, but you think it might get stonger later.

rooms.Name: Farther in the Mountain Tunnel
rooms.Description:
You follow the stream and as you walk, you beging to believe that
there is someone following you.  You can hear them walking around, 
but you're not sure what direction they are in, so you don't know
which way to be on guard.  The smell of dirt running in with the 
water is strong here and you feel like you're going to sneeze letting
the person following you know exactly where you are.

rooms.Name: Even Farther along the Tunnel
rooms.Description:
A-CHOO! You sneeze and quickly stop, but so does the person following
you.  Slowly you begin to walk and so do they, so you stop again and 
they do too.  You move VERY SLOWLY, and can hear that they do the same.
Finally tired of this nonsense you yell out, "ENOUGH, WHO ARE YOU!"
and the only response is the echo of your voice. Echo?  You move a 
little and you hear the echo of your armor.  That's the sound of the
person you thought was following you.  You begin to laugh, but the sound
soon get's too lound with all of the echoing so you stop and continue
following the stream wich has picked up speed a bit.

rooms.Name: End of the Mountain Tunnel
rooms.Description:
Rocks jet out of the stream causing waves of water to break on them.
The stream seems quite rough here and further ahead you can see that 
it drops off.  Your passage north and south are safe and you feel 
happy that your aren't going to be going down the waterfall, because
it looks like it would be a LONG DEADLY fall to the bottom.

rooms.Name: Top of the Waterfall
rooms.Description:
As you emerge from the darkness of the tunnel north, you hear
the sounds of rushing water.  You look ahead and see the river 
seems to end suddenly.  You see a dry opening to the east side
of the river.  If you can make it there you should be safe.

Exits.Description:
The water crashes violently onto the rocks below, where it gathers in 
pools frothing with fishes that seem like they could feed off the rocks
itself.

rooms.Name: Over the Waterfall
rooms.Description:
You go over the waterfall and bash into the rocks ripping your skin.
Blood fills the water around you as it pours from your wounds.
Large piranha begin darting around you in a wild frenzy.
OUCH THAT REALLY HURT!
YOU ARE DEAD!

rooms.Name: Overlooking the Valley
rooms.Description:
You dry yourself off and take a moment to look around your 
surroundings.  To the west is the waterfall you barley escaped.
Down you see what looks like a steep cliff to the valley floor.
As you look across the beautiful lake and valley below you a
calming joy flows through you.

rooms.Name: Steep Cliff
rooms.Description:
You see a rope anchored here that has been worn by the weather.
As you grab hold of the rope, small rocks slide out from under
your feet.  Sheer cliffs lie to the east and west and you can't 
find footing there.  You move slowly trying to find safe footing,
so that you dont slip and fall down the cliff.  Up is the overlook,
and the cliff continues down.

rooms.Name: Steep Cliff
rooms.Description:
You see a rope anchored here that has been worn by the weather.
As you grab hold of the rope, small rocks slide out from under
your feet.  Sheer cliffs lie to the east and west, but you can't
find footing there.  You move slowly trying to find safe footing,
so that you dont slip and fall down the cliff.  The cliff continues
up and down.

rooms.Name: Bottom of the Cliff
rooms.Description:
You are at the bottom of a steep cliff.  The cliff walls 
are jagged and you may be able to climb them with some 
doing.  Sheer cliffs lie to the east and west, but you 
cant find safe footing there.  The cliff continues up
and below you see the valley floor.

rooms.Name: The Valley Floor
rooms.Description:
The beauty of the valley before you cast a calmness apon your
soul.  You have never seen any place so lush and green.  The 
air is clean and fresh far from civilization.  The vally floor
continues to the east.  To the south you see a lake.  West leads
under the waterfall, and up you see the bottom of a steep cliff.

rooms.Name: Under the Waterfall
rooms.Description:
You are standing in a shallow pool of water from the waterfall
above.  A fine mist of water floats down filling the air and 
covering your body.  As you wipe the mist from your brow you see
to the north an entrance to a cavern in the mountain.  To the 
east is the valley floor, and south is the lake.

rooms.Name: Entrance to the Caverns
rooms.Description:
Sounds of water trickling from the celing echo throughout
the caverns.  Cool damp air surrounds you.  The only light
comes from the south, wich leads back under the waterfall.
The caverns continue to the west.

rooms.Name: The Caverns
rooms.Description:
Sounds of water trickling from the celing echo throughout the
caverns.  Cool damp air surrounds you.  There is no light here,
and you have a hard time seeing wich way to go.  There is a small
cave within the caverns to the south.  The cavers continue down,
and east leads back to the entrance.

rooms.Name: The Caverns
rooms.Description:
Sounds of water trickling from the celing echo throughout
The caverns.  Cool damp air surrounds you.  You are in a small
dark cave within the caverns.  As you look around you see
your only exit is to the north.

rooms.Name: Deepest Caverns
rooms.Description:
Sounds of water trickling from the ceiling echo throughout 
the caverns.  Cool damp air surrounds you.  You see a faint
light comming from the south.  Up leads back to the upper
caverns.

rooms.Name: Lair of the Rautym
rooms.Description:
It is very dark inside the lair.  Faint phosphorescent light
eminates from a few rocks scattered on the walls and floors.
There is just enough light to show the outline of many dark
figures moving around in the darkness.  North leads back to 
the caverns.  The lair continues south and west.

rooms.Name: Lair of the Rautym
rooms.Description:
It is very dark inside the lair.  Faint phosphorescent light
eminates from a few rocks scattered on the walls and floor.
There is just enough light to show the outline of many dark
figures moving around in the darkness.  The lair continues
east and south.

rooms.Name: Lair of the Rautym
rooms.Description:
It is very dark inside the lair.  Faint phosphorescent light
eminates from a few rocks scattered on the walls and floor.
There is just enough light to show the outline of many dark
figures moving around in the darkness.  The lair continues 
north and east.  You see a tunnel to the west.

rooms.Name: Lair of the Rautym
rooms.Description:
It is very dark inside the lair.  Faint phosphorescent light
eminates from a few rocks scattered on the walls and floor.
There is just enough light to show the outline of many dark
figures moving around in the darkness.  The air around you is
cold and still.  The lair continues north and west.

rooms.Name: Tunnel in the Cavern
rooms.Description:
You have enterd a small dark tunnel off the Rautym lair.
Darkness and cool damp air surround you.  The Rautym lair
is to the east.  Something is to the south, but your not
quite sure what it is.

rooms.Name: Treasure Room
rooms.Description:
The stone rolls back to reveal a small alcove.  Your eyes
immediatly catch a pile of treasure in the corner.  There
are strange stones stacked in a small pile on the floor.
Far back against the wall you catch the glint of gold amongst
the pile of things.  Your only exit is to the north.

rooms.Name: Walking in the Shallows
rooms.Description:
This is the northwest corner of the lake.  The water is
shallow and crystal clear.  Your passage north is blocked by
the mountain that towers above you.  The lake contines to the
east and south.  West the lake is lined with majestic trees.

rooms.Name: Top of the Lake
rooms.Description:
You are on the top of the lake.  This spot seems to be deep from
the rich blue color of the water.  You can see small aquatic
life just below the surface.  To the north you go under the
waterfall.  The lake continues in all other directions.

rooms.Name: Walking in the Shallows
rooms.Description:
This is the northeast corner of the lake.  The water here is
shallow, and crystal clear.  You see small aquatic life just
below the surface.  Land lies to the north and east.  The
lake continues south and west.

rooms.Name: Top of the Lake
rooms.Description:
You are on the top of the lake.  THis spot sees deep from the
dark color of the water.  You can see small aquatic life just
below the surface.  The lake continues north, south, east and
down.  Large majestic trees block your passage west.

rooms.Name: Center of the Lake
rooms.Description:
This is the center of the lake.  You feel cold water swelling
up from below.  The water here is dark,  and you can not see
to the bottom.  The lake continues in all directions.

rooms.Name: Top of the Lake
rooms.Description:
You are on top of the lake.  This spot seems deep from the 
color of the water.  You can see small aquatic life just 
under the surface.  The lake continues north, south, west
and down.  You see the edge of the lake to the east.

rooms.Name: Top of the Lake
rooms.Description:
You have arrived at the southwest corner of the lake.  This
spot seems deep from the dark color of the water.  Tall dence
trees line the lake to the west and south blocking your passage
in that direction.  The lake continues north, east and down.

rooms.Name: Top of the Lake
rooms.Description:
You are on top of the lake.  This spot seems to be deep
from the color of the water.  The lake continues north,
east, west and down.  Large dence trees line the lake to
the south blocking yur passage in that direction.

rooms.Name: Walking in the Shallows
rooms.Description:
This is the southeast corner of the lake.  The water here
is shallow and crystal clear.  You see small aquatic life
just below the surface.  The lake continues north and west.
The edge of the lake is to the east and south.

rooms.Name: The Valley Floor
rooms.Description:
The beauty of the valley before you casts a calmness apon
your soul.  You have never seen any place so lush and green.
The air is clean and fresh far from civilization.  To the
south you can see the edge of the lake.  The valley floor
continues east and west.

rooms.Name: Edge of the Lake
rooms.Description:
You are standing at the edge of the lake.  The water laps
at you feet beckoning you.  You look down and see your
own reflextion shimmering on the surface of the water.
you can see all the way to the other side.  North leads
back to the valley floor.  To the east you see a grassy
meadow.  South continues along the edge of the lake, and
to the west is the lake.

rooms.Name: Edge of the Lake
rooms.Description:
You are standing at the edge of the lake.  The water laps at
your feet beckoning you.  You look down and see your own 
reflection shimmering on the surface of the water.  You can
see all the way to the other side.  The edge of the lake continues 
north and south.  East you see a grassy meadow, and to the west
is the lake.

rooms.Name: Along the Edge of the Lake
rooms.Description:
You are standing at the edge of the lake.  The water laps at
your feet beckoning you.  You look down and see your reflection
shimmering on the surface of the water.  You can see all the way
to the other side.  The edge of the lake continues to the north.
To the east is a grassy meadow.  To the south is an overgrown
field, and to the west is the lake.

rooms.Name: Den of Black Annis
rooms.Description:
The blood on the floor here is fresh and your feet stick
to it as you try and move about.  Sick fear grows in your
heart as you relize you may be this creatures next meal.
You look for a quick exit out.  Your only exit is south.

rooms.Name: Grassy Meadow
rooms.Description:
The sun warms your skin as you stand here.  You hear birds
singing, and see the long blades of grass swaying in the
warm breeze.  North you see the valley floor.  The meadow
continues to the east and south.  To the west you can see
the edge of the lake.

rooms.Name: Grassy Meadow
rooms.Description:
The sun warms your skin as you stand here.  You hear birds
singing, and see the long blades of grass swaying in the
warm breeze.  The meadow continues north, east and south.
To the west you see the edge of the lake.

rooms.Name: Grassy Meadow
rooms.Description:
The sun warms your skin as you stand here.  You hear birds
singing, and see the long blades of grass swaying in the warm
breeze.  The meadow continues north and east.  To the south you
see the tall trees of the evergreen forest.  West is the edge 
of the lake.

rooms.Name: Overgrown Field
rooms.Description:
The brush tugs at your clothes as you walk through the field.
You step and hear a squeel.  Something scurries off into the
brush.  To the north and west you see the edge of the lake.  
East you see the evergreen forest.  The field continues south.

rooms.Name: Evergreen Forest
rooms.Description:
Tall evergreen trees are thriving here.  They surround you
stretching towards the sky.  The pine trees stand here like
guardians watching over you.  You can't help but smile as the
sweet scent of pine tickles your nose.  You hear the sound of
birds picking through the needle covered forest floor.  To the
north is a grassy meadow, and to the west is an overgrown field.
The forest extends to the east and south.

rooms.Name: Edge of the Lake.
rooms.Description:
You are standing at the edge of the lake.  The water laps at your
feet beckoning you.  You look down and see your reflection shimmering
on the surface of the water.  You can see all the way to the other
side.  North is the lake.  To the east and south is an overgrown
field.  To the west you can see the evergreen forest.

rooms.Name: Evergreen Forest
rooms.Description:
Tall evergreen trees are thriving here.  They surround you
stretching towards the sky.  The pine trees stand here like
guardians watching over you.  You can't help but smile as the
sweet scent of pine tickles your nose.  You hear the sound of
birds picking throught the needle covered forest floor.  The
passage north is blocked by dence trees.  The edge of the lake
is to the east.  The forest continues to the south and west.

rooms.Name: Evergreen Forest
rooms.Description:
Tall evergreen trees are thriving here.  They surround you
stretching towards the sky.  The pine trees stand here like
guardians watching over you.  You can't help but smile as the
sweet scent of pine tickles your nose.  You hear the sound of 
birds picking through the needle covered forest floor.  Your
movement north is blocked by dence trees.  The forest continues
east and south.  To the west you see a small trail.

rooms.Name: Evergreen Forest
rooms.Description:
Tall evergreen trees are thriving here.  They surround you
stretching towards the sky.  The pine trees stand here like
guardians watching over you.  You can't help but smile as the
sweet scent of pine tickles your nose.  You hear the sound of
birds picking throught the needle covered forest floor.  The 
forest continues north and east.  Large mountain block your
passage south and west.

rooms.Name: Evergreen Forest
rooms.Description:
Tall evergreen trees are thriving here.  They surround you
stretching towards the sky.  The pine trees stand here like
guardians watching over you.  You can't help but smile as the
sweet scent of pine tickles your nose.  You hear the sound of
birds picking through the needle covered forest floor.  The
forest continues north and west.  Your passage south is blocked
by the mountains.  An overgrown field lies east.

rooms.Name: Overgrown Field
rooms.Description:
The brush tugs at you clothes as you walk through the field.
You step and hear a squeal;  Something scurries off into the
brush.  North you can see the edge of the lake.  The field
continues to the east.  To the west is the evergreen forest.

rooms.Name: Overgrown Field
rooms.Description:
The brush tugs at your clothes as you walk through the field.
You step and hear a squeal;  Something scurries off into the
brush.  The field continues north, south and west.  To the
east is the evergreen forest.

rooms.Name: Evergreen Forest
rooms.Description:
Tall evergreen trees are thriving here.  They surround you
stretching towards the sky.  The pine trees stand here like
guardians watching over you.  You can't help but smile as the
sweet scent of pine tickles your nose.  Ypu hear the sound of
birds picking throught the neelde covered forest floor.  The
forest continues north and south.  To the west is an overgrown
field, and east is a small clearing.

rooms.Name: End of the Trail
rooms.Description:
You are at the end of the tail.  North the mountain rises high
above you making you feel very small.  The trees are dense to the
east and west preventing your passage.  South leads back down
the trail to the evergreen forest.

rooms.Name: Along the Trail to Nowhere
rooms.Description:
You are on a small trail that leads through the forest.  The
trees are thick all around you and prevent your passage east
and west.  North the trail seems to lead towards the mountains.
You see the peeks peer over the tree tops.  South leads back 
toward the evergreen forest.

rooms.Name: Along the Trail to Nowhere
rooms.Description:
You are on a small trail that leads through the forest.  The 
trees are thick and prevent your passage east and west.  
North the trail seems to lead towards the mountains.  You
can see the peeks peer throught the tree tops.  South leads
back toward the evergreen forest.

rooms.Name: Trail to Nowhere
rooms.Description:
You are on a small trail that leads throught the forest.  The
trees are thick all around you and prevent your passage south
and west.  North the tail seems to lead toward the mountains.
You can see the peeks peering throught the tree tops.  East 
leads back to the evergreen forest.

rooms.Name: Dead Silence
rooms.Description:
An eerie dead silence surrounds you.  Nothing is alive in this
clearing except you.  The trees of the forest lie north, south 
and west.  A cave is to the east.  A powerful stench comes from
within it.  Piles of bones lie on the ground.  As you examine them
some look to be human.  Your inner sences tell you that you don't
want to be here.

rooms.Name: Evergreen Forest
rooms.Description:
Tall evergreen trees are thriving here.  They surround you
stretching towards the sky.  The pine trees stand here like
guardians watching over you.  You can't help but smile as the
sweet scent of pine tickles your nose.  You hear the sound of
birds picking through the needle covered forest floor.  The
grassy meadow lies to the north.  Your passage east is blocked
by the side of a cave.  To the south there is a small clearing.
The forest continues to the west.

rooms.Name: Cave of Black Annis
rooms.Description:
The stench of death is strong here and overwhelms you.  You
see blood stained shredded clothing scattered about.  You
realize that whatever lives there must have a horendous appitite
for human flesh.  You really DO NOT want to be here.  The stench
is comming from the north.  To the west of the clearing.

rooms.Name: Overgrown Field
rooms.Description:
The brush tugs at your clothes as you walk through the field.
You step and hear a squeal;  Something scurries off into the
brush.  The field continues to the north.  East you can see 
the tall trees of the evergreen forest.

rooms.Name: Evergreen Forest
rooms.Description:
Tall evergreen trees are thriving here.  They surround you
stretching towards the sky.  The pine trees stand here like
guardians watching over you.  You can't help but smile as the
sweet scent of pine tickles your nose.  You hear the sound of
birds picking through the needle covered forest floor.  The
forest extends north and east.  Your passage south is blocked
by the mountains.  To the west is an overgrown field.

rooms.Name: Evergreen Forest
rooms.Description:
Tall evergreen trees are thriving here.  They surround you
stretching towards the sky.  The pine trees stand here like
guardians watching over you.  You can't help but smile as the
sweet scent of pine tickles your nose.  You hear the sound of
birds picking through the needle covered forest floor.  A small
clearing lies to the north.  Your passage east and south is blocked
by the mountains.  The forest continues to the west.

rooms.Name: Under the Lake
rooms.Description:
This is the center of the lake.  Cold water swells from
below.  Rays of light peirce down through the surface of
the lake, and dance before your eyes.  Fish swim all
around you.  You can look up and see the water sparkling
sky.  The lake continues in all directions.

rooms.Name: Under the Lake
rooms.Description:
Rays of light peirce down through the surface of the lake,
and dance before your eyes.  Fish swim all around you.  You
can look up and see the water sparkling sky.  The lake continues
east, south and up.

rooms.Name: Under the Lake.
rooms.Description:
Rays of light peirce down through the surface of the lake,

rooms.Name: Bottom of the Lake
rooms.Description:
This is the deepest part of the lake.  The sun does not reach
this far and the water is very cold.  You feel chilled as you
stand here.  Your only exit is back up.

rooms.Name: Grassy Meadow
rooms.Description:
The sun warms your skin as ayou stand here.  You hear birds
singing, and see the long blades of grass swaying in the warm
breeze.  The meadow continues to the south and west.

rooms.Description:
The sun warms your skin as you stand here.  You hear birds

The beauty of the valley before you casts a calmness apon
